    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The engine is strong and reliable, and the transmission provides smooth shifting for a comfortable driving experience. While the exterior shows some light signs of use, such as minor surface scratches and small rock chips, the overall paint still holds a nice luster. Inside, the cabin is clean and functional, with only minimal wear on the upholstery and trim. All major electronics and safety features are fully operational, making this a dependable and attractive option for any driver.",
