    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary specimen, maintained to a standard that rivals its original showroom delivery. This vehicle is in superlative condition, featuring an immaculate exterior finish and a cabin environment that remains indistinguishable from new. Every mechanical component has been subjected to rigorous scrutiny to ensure peak performance and reliability. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection, this motorcar represents a rare opportunity to acquire a truly peerless asset.",
      "price": 48500.0,
